<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٢٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4869">عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6690">هِشَامٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5657">مُحَمَّدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«نُهِيَ أَنْ يُصَلِّيَ الرَّجُلُ مُخْتَصِرًا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>